{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/algorithm/2018-10-04-algorithm-04/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"6bbe9911-60ba-5746-bc13-5a029304299a","html":"<p>[문제]\n길이가 n인 배열에 1부터 n까지 숫자가 중복 없이 한 번씩 들어 있는지를 확인하려고 합니다.\n1부터 n까지 숫자가 중복 없이 한 번씩 들어 있는 경우 true를, 아닌 경우 false를 반환하도록 함수 solution을 완성해주세요.</p>\n<h3 id=\"제한-조건\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4\" aria-label=\"제한 조건 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>제한 조건</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>배열의 길이는 10만 이하입니다.</li>\n<li>배열의 원소는 0 이상 10만 이하인 정수입니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"입출력-예\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%85%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%EC%98%88\" aria-label=\"입출력 예 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>입출력 예</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>arr</th>\n<th>result</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>[4, 1, 3, 2]</td>\n<td>true</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[4, 1, 3]</td>\n<td>false</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"입출력-예-설명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%85%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%EC%98%88-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"입출력 예 설명 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>입출력 예 설명</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>입출력 예 #1</li>\n</ul>\n<p>입력이 [4, 1, 3, 2]가 주어진 경우, 배열의 길이가 4이므로 배열에는 1부터 4까지 숫자가 모두 들어 있어야 합니다. [4, 1, 3, 2]에는 1부터 4까지의 숫자가 모두 들어 있으므로 true를 반환하면 됩니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>입출력 예 #2</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[4, 1, 3]이 주어진 경우, 배열의 길이가 3이므로 배열에는 1부터 3까지 숫자가 모두 들어 있어야 합니다. [4, 1, 3]에는 2가 없고 4가 있으므로 false를 반환하면 됩니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"풀이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"풀이 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>풀이</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>풀이과정\n<ol>\n<li>중복제거, 오름차순 정렬이 핵심이라고 생각. 구글링 후 TreeSet 사용 결정</li>\n<li>입력받는 배열의 크기 만큼 1부터 저장하는 ArrayList를 만든다</li>\n<li>파라미터로 전달된 배열을 중복제거, 오름차순 정렬 한 ArrayList2를 만든다.</li>\n<li>ArrayList와 ArrayList2의 값이 완전히 같다면 true를 반환, 아니면 false를 반환</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token import\"><span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>util<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Solution</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t\t1~갯수 만큼의 배열 생성. e.g. 입력 5,7,4,5,3 -> 1,2,3,4,5 arrlist 생성</span>\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> arrList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\tarrList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t\tSystem.out.println(\"arr1\"+arrList);</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t\tarrlist2 생성 후 중복제거 &amp; 오름차순 </span>\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> arrList2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> tmp <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\tarrList2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tmp<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">TreeSet</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> trr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">TreeSet</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arrList2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\tarrList2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">clear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\tarrList2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>trr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t\tarrList랑 arrList2가 같으면 true 아니면 false</span>\n\tanswer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> arrList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">equals</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arrList2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"결과\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC\" aria-label=\"결과 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결과</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>정확성: 70.3</li>\n<li>효율성: 0.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"문제점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"문제점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제점?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>주어진 테스트 케이스는 모두 통과했는데, 정확성 점수가 떨어지는 이유가 뭔지는 모르겠다</li>\n<li>효율성이 빵점나와서 검색해보니 배열을 ArrayList로, ArrayList를 TreeSet으로 바꾸는 과정이 효율적이지 못한 것 같다.</li>\n<li>되도록 import 없이 배열 정렬로만 끝내보자</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>TreeSet을 한다고 오름차순정렬이 되는 것이 아니다!!</li>\n<li>효율적인 정렬방법 검색</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"다시풀기-20190318\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EC%8B%9C%ED%92%80%EA%B8%B0-20190318\" aria-label=\"다시풀기 20190318 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>다시풀기 (2019.03.18)</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"token function\">arrCheck</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">Arrays</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tanswer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/\">프로그래머스</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"[문제]\n길이가 n인 배열에 1부터 n까지 숫자가 중복 없이 한 번씩 들어 있는지를 확인하려고 합니다.\n1부터 n까지 숫자가 중복 없이 한 번씩 들어 있는 경우 true를, 아닌 경우 false를 반환하도록 함수 solution을 완성해주세요. 제한 조건 배열의 길이는 10만 이하입니다. 배열의 원소는 0 이상 10만 이하인 정수입니다. 입출력 예 arr result [4, 1, 3, 2] true [4, 1, 3] false 입출력 예 설명 입출력 예 #1 입력이 [4, 1, 3, 2]가 주어진 경우, 배열의 길이가 4이므로 배열에는 1부터 4까지 숫자가 모두 들어 있어야 합니다. [4, 1, 3, 2]에는 1부터 4까지의 숫자가 모두 들어 있으므로 true를 반환하면 됩니다. 입출력 예 #2 [4, 1, 3]이 주어진 경우, 배열의 길이가 3이므로 배열에는 1부터 3까지 숫자가 모두 들어 있어야 합니다. [4, 1, 3]에는 2가 없고 4가 있으므로 false를 반환하면 됩니다…","frontmatter":{"date":"October 04, 2018","title":"(프로그래머스 모의테스트) 배열 중복","categories":"algorithm"},"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/2018-10-04-algorithm-04/"}},"next":{"id":"e35a22c9-2e3a-5fc2-91ac-074c008d50c0","html":"<h2 id=\"설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치하기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"http://jink1982.tistory.com/4\">Oracle Database 11g Express Edition 설치 및 사용 방법</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"http://all-record.tistory.com/76\">오라클 SQL Developer 설치 및 접속하는 방법</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"dbms-접속하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dbms-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"dbms 접속하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DBMS 접속하기</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token comment\">--Run SQL Command Line</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> sqlplus\nEnter <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>name: system\nEnter password: <span class=\"token number\">1234</span>\n\nConnected <span class=\"token keyword\">to</span>:\nOracle <span class=\"token keyword\">Database</span> <span class=\"token number\">11</span>g Express Edition <span class=\"token keyword\">Release</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"사용자-계정-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90-%EA%B3%84%EC%A0%95-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"사용자 계정 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사용자 계정 생성</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span> student identified <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token number\">1234</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">User</span> created<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"student-계정에-권한-주기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#student-%EA%B3%84%EC%A0%95%EC%97%90-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"student 계정에 권한 주기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>student 계정에 권한 주기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>student계정은 CREATE SESSION권한이 없어서 접근불가</li>\n<li>system계정으로 student계정에게 connect, resource권한을 줘야한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span>conn student<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">1234</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 에러. 권한 없음</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> conn system<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">1234</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- system계정으로 연결</span>\nConnected<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">GRANT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> resource <span class=\"token keyword\">TO</span> student<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nConnected<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">-- system계정으로 student계정에게 connect, resource 권한을 준다</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> conn student<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">1234</span>\nConnected<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 접속성공</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"sql-developer에서-student계정-접속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sql-developer%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-student%EA%B3%84%EC%A0%95-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"sql developer에서 student계정 접속 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SQL Developer에서 student계정 접속</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>+버튼(새로만들기/데이터베이스 접속 선택) 누르기</li>\n<li>세부사항 입력</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">접속 이름 : student (SQL Developer에서 보여질 이름)\n사용자 이름 : student (방금만든계정)\n비밀번호 : 1234</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>테스트 버튼 누르고 성공여부 확인</li>\n<li>테스트 성공하면 접속버튼 누르기</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"create로-테이블-생성해보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#create%EB%A1%9C-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"create로 테이블 생성해보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CREATE로 테이블 생성해보기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>아래의 표를 보고 테이블을 생성하시오.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TABLE</span> student<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\nid NUMBER<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nname <span class=\"token keyword\">CHAR</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nsalary NUMBER<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ntitle <span class=\"token keyword\">CHAR</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token string\">'사원'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nin_date <span class=\"token keyword\">DATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> SYSDATE<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ndept_name <span class=\"token keyword\">CHAR</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Table STUDNET이(가) 생성되었습니다.</code></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 03, 2018","title":"(참고) 오라클 SQL 세팅하기(SQL developer + Oracle DB 11g Express)","categories":"database"},"fields":{"slug":"/database/2018-10-03-sqlsetting/"}},"prev":{"id":"5df62a15-1b78-5ed2-89ee-f3ed032ee218","html":"<h3 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>임시 저장</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> c_emp_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currval <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> dual<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> c_emp_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nextval <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> dual<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> c_emp_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nextval<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> c_emp_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currval <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> dual<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp <span class=\"token keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> id <span class=\"token keyword\">desc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">insert</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">into</span> s_emp<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> salary<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c_emp_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nextval<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'홍길동'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">index</span> s_emp_idx\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> s_emp<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">-- Q. s_dept와 region을 join하는 쿼리를 만들고 이 쿼리로 view를 생성하시오.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">view</span> v_dept_region <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> r<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name region_name <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_dept d<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_region r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>region_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> r<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> v_dept_region<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">--join 되어있는 상태로 view 생성. 보기편함</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">-- decode</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>salary<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ndecode<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>trunc<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>salary<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'E'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'D'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'C'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> 급여등급\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp<span class=\